<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="uuid" content="32c0d6d0-2f96-464f-a171-4eba09b052a7"/><meta name="last-change-date" content="2021-03-08T21:26:05.3810000+08:00"/><meta name="create-date" content="2021-03-08T21:26:05.3810000+08:00"/><meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /><title>查找与替换</title><style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style></head><body style=" font-family:'DejaVu Sans'; font-size:16pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600; color:#000000;">查找</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" text-decoration: underline;">查找字符</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">f{char} t{char} (查找下一个字符）</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">F{char} T{char} (查找上一个字符)</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">; (重复)   , (回退)</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" text-decoration: underline;">查找匹配项</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">/pattern (查找下一个匹配项)</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">* (查找光标所在单词的所有匹配项)</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">?pattern (查找上一个匹配项)</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">n (重复)   N (回退)</p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">替换</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:{作用范围}s/{目标}/{替换}/{替换的标志}</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">最简单的几种：</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:s/pattern/replacement    当前行第一个pattern换为replacement</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:%s/pattern/replacement   (全文所有行第一个pattern换为replacement)</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:n1(0),n2($)s/pattern/replacement   (选定区域每行第一个pattern换为replacement)</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:s/pattern/replacement/g    当前行全部pattern换为replacement</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:s/pattern/replacement/gI		当前行全部pattern换为replacement(大小写敏感,，i为不敏感)</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Noto Sans CJK SC';">:s/pattern/replacement/gcI		当前行全部pattern换为replacement(大小写敏感，i为不敏感)，每次确认是否替换</span></p></body></html>